## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Backend Improvements

#### [MODIFY] [notification.controller.ts](file:///d:/iDesk-main/apps/backend/src/modules/notifications/notification.controller.ts)
- Add `POST /notifications/bulk-delete` — batch delete endpoint (accepts array of IDs)
- Add `POST /notifications/bulk-read` — batch mark-as-read endpoint (accepts array of IDs)
- Add pagination support to `GET /notifications` — `page`, `limit`, return `{ data, total, page, pageSize }`

